Short:    Picasso96 board freemem checker!
Author:   grio (ogrio@o2.pl)
Uploader: grio (ogrio@o2.pl)
Version:  0.3
Type:     gfx/board
Required: OS3.0, CPU 020+, Picasso96 and supported GFX Board.


Introduction:
P96Mem it's small tool which give you posibility of checking free memory
on GFX Board.Check result is saved as environment variable.
Why i wrote this tool ? Well , i want display size of free GFX Board mem
on Workbench titlebar with MCP feature "ChangeWorkbenchTitle".

